.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, dancing, rock-climbing, video-games, fishing
5 different games are played: domino, scrabble, chess, canasta, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: readingmaster, zombie, spy, martial-arts, sports
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person playing domino is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing
2. the person playing swedish is the owner of the dog
3. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking coffee
6. the person watching spy movies is the owner of the bird
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person watching zombie movies
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person playing canasta is on the far left
10. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies
12. the person watching readingmaster movies is the person drinking beer
13. the person playing chess is the person watching martial-arts movies
14. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading
15. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
